about.summary: Create, store, access, and manipulate massive matrices. Matrices are allocated to shared memory and may use memory-mapped files.  Packages 'biganalytics', 'bigtabulate', 'synchronicity', and 'bigalgebra' provide advanced functionality.

name: r-bigmemory
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '4.5.33' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-bigmemory
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: bigmemory_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/bigmemory_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/bigmemory/bigmemory_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7237d9785d8ce3eab4e36ad3ce2c95cbae926326031661b4f237b7517f4b9479

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1003
  skip: true  # [win32]
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{posix}}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{posix}}sed               # [win]
    - {{posix}}grep              # [win]
    - {{posix}}autoconf
    - {{posix}}automake          # [not win]
    - {{posix}}automake-wrapper  # [win]
    - {{posix}}pkg-config
    - {{posix}}make
    - {{posix}}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-bh
    - r-rcpp
    - r-bigmemory.sri
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{native}}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-bh
    - r-rcpp
    - r-bigmemory.sri

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('bigmemory')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('bigmemory')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/kaneplusplus/bigmemory
  license: LGPL-3 | Apache 2.0
  summary: Create, store, access, and manipulate massive matrices. Matrices are allocated to
    shared memory and may use memory-mapped files.  Packages 'biganalytics', 'bigtabulate',
    'synchronicity', and 'bigalgebra' provide advanced functionality.
  license_family: LGPL

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
